data.description: Looking for the perfect blend of a lovely ranch-style with dual-living spaces on a large-sized, manicured lot? This elegant home has 4 bedrooms, 2.75 bath and delivers 2,548 sqft nicely nested on its 1.27-acre, irrigated spread in the appealing Bountiful Acres. The approximate 600-foot private guest studio has 1 bedroom, 1 bath, a living room, and a kitchenette. Ideal set-up for two independent-style residences under the same roof: Think guesthouse, VRBO passive-income, extended family, or assisted living set up. Full-fenced, lush green lawn off the walk-out deck that overlooks the beauty of Black Canyon horizon, Storm King, and San Juans. HOA provides for irrigation water, and it allows for RVs and trailers. Well-kept inside and out and move-in ready just as soon as you are, including turnkey with furnishings. BONUS: Seller is now offering $10,000 in seller concessions to be used for interest rate buy-down, loan closing costs, or upgrades that the buyer desires!
